orangelight.title: Open Dataset page should link to POD dataset, not main Events list

comments.body:
I took a look at Lib-Jobs and it looks like there's a way to download at least the latest version of a file, but I couldn't get it to work for the POD dataset. The specs, so I assume this is an access control issue, so we might need to open up access to this particular dataset.

The other option would be to update the process to copy the files to a separate directory and expose that using an nginx directory listing or something like that, where there wouldn't be access controls.

Either of those seem like reasonable ways to let anonymous users actually download the most recent POD dataset.
